text: Ken(ny) or Kenneth Green(e) may refer to: ==Sportspeople== *Ken Green (golfer) (born 1958), American golfer *Ken Green (footballer, born 1929), English footballer (Grimsby Town) *Ken Green (footballer, born 1924) (1924–2001), English footballer (Birmingham City) *Ken Green (basketball, born 1959), American basketball player *Ken Greene (born 1956), American football ==Others== *Kenneth Green (physicist) (1911–1997), accelerator physicist *Kenny Green (basketball, born 1964), formerly of Wake Forest University *Kenny Green (basketball, born 1967), formerly of the University of Rhode Island *Kenny Green (voice actor), American voice actor for FUNimation Entertainment *Kenny Greene (1969–2001), musician *Kenneth P.
